overview: "Twink Toy Story 2" breaks the bounds of twink videos by showing you twink action filmed entirely in High Definition Wide Screen. Featuring returning twinks Jon Jameson & Jordan Mason, you will also be introduced to Chase Graham, Jason Kolie, Cameron Philips and Jacob Daniels. Sean Hardick also makes a special appearance in this spectacular sequel. You will run out of tissue watching these twink toy boyz with their ultra smooth bodies as they rim, are rough, spank and swallow.
title: Twink Toy Story 2
